<div style=3D"font-size:10px;margin-top:1px">Anzeige</div><p>Heights, bisec=
ting lines, median lines, perpendicular bisectors and symmetry axes coincid=
e. To these, the equilateral triangle is axially symmetric. They meet with =
centroid, circumcircle and incircle center in one point. To this, the equil=
ateral triangle is rotationally symmetric at a rotation of 120=C2=B0or mult=
iples of this, so it has the order 3.</p>
